Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.83,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Slowly, quietly, floating by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:35.52,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}Gently fading into the distant bright sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:44.39,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}More fickle than the wind,\N my goal is beyond it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:47.48,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Let's go together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:53.12,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a breath and skip along,\N the world's spring breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:58.67,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun brings all our smiles together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:06.22,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Between "good morning" and "good bye" it's just us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.88,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}We can do whatever we want
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:15.98,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}The sunlight shining down,\N a brand new sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:21.72,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning arch we promised to meet at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:29.52,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Waving your hand at me,\N let me make today a special day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:32.66,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,600)}Let's start by talking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:45.91,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Next to me in the sunset, a silhouette tall as me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:54.72,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of another fun day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:23:01.89,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got so much unending stuff to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:09.23,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's time for us to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:16.41,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, I'll text you later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:23.70,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's page is about all our smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:31.00,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, thanks as always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:39.55,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy we could be together today too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:46.72,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Humhumhum, the wind and my heart are humming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:53.98,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}At the next corner, I'll turn around and say "Bye bye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation's just about to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then school starts again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:17.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:20.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to see everyone in class again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in class?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there, Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:30.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, I didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:32.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:37.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always have boys around you. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:41.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:45.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone ever confessed to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:49.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:50.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he likes things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:00.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of weird for someone to like candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he likes candles like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:47.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\an5\fs64\fad(400,0)\be18\pos(630,488)\c&HA6F9C1&\3c&HA7D9B3&}Summer Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:49.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:56.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they have this fireworks show every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a lot of booths too. Very lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and it's this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could all wear yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:16.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's fine once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you want to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:27.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot. I don't want to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we go for some karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:36.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke? Sounds fun. I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Yuuko, you like karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can pretty much sing any of my ringtones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like, Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:51.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at this place it has to be the jambalaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then ramen for reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:57.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then their parfaits come with so much ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Weren't we going for karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of small.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll order some food and drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Melon soda for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grapefruit juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru? A drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Iced tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:27.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, hello. We'd like to order now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:29.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they've got this month's new songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:32.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One iced tea, one melon soda, and one grapefruit juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put mine in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:36.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And one jambalaya and french fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:42.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.34,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me summer breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.58,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.89,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me summer breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:06.41,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,My love is feeling the breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.97,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me summer breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.10,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Gently now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.41,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me summer breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:20.17,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,A summer dream taking off with you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:28.55,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking off with you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:35.09,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me summer breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko's got a voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru looks really serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she picky or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take your time picking a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:02.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you staring at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:14.09,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,A cute alarm clock, gravity pulling me back to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:19.52,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring-ring, snore-snore, another day slipping out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:25.18,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting with my best friend over the best scrunchie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:30.34,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gets in the last word? There, you just lost it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:35.70,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tell everyone about this strange magic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:40.82,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Using words that people might spread around
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:44.96,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,(3, 2, 1, say!) Playful, melodical, beauty, bang-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.92,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,With a big smile
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, finished your staring contest with the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you want this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll enter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. Entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:21.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mic! The mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My jambalaya's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:54.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still hot, so please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grapefruit juice over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The melon soda is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't want to sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I entered it without asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:19.97,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly fading away into the twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:25.35,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,A young country girl's innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:30.84,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it a love never to be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:39.14,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see you one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put some passion into that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just two more songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:56.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I sing two more songs, I can eat eight fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:04.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tooru, didn't you like that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I've never sung it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:16.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, it's turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:51.22,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold hands together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:55.33,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other side of the hill
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:59.20,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one, two, three
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.30,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,And even more fun things
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:15.37,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,A white blanket
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:19.32,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,A big-eyed puppet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:22.68,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,A polka dot skirt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:27.00,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't split that with you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:31.50,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you fall, even if you cry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:34.73,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:39.34,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.06,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:46.03,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold hands together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:49.86,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,And walk straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:53.81,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one, two, three
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:57.99,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,And even more fun things
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only three left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't really work out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no one's singing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll sing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish eating before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then my next song will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one was there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:30.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the song is kind of stuffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:37.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan, don't sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:42.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:11:59.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sing karaoke with Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:27.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke sure was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get better at singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:37.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were talking about how to get better on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:44.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs56\pos(374,79)\3c&HAC62DE&\c&H9BF4ED&\fad(200,0)}For {\c&HDDA7FF&}next {\c&HCBF5CD&}time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:44.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs56\pos(374,300)\3c&HAC62DE&\c&HA0FFC3&\fad(200,0)}Pa{\c&HBDF3F4&}rt {\c&HF3CBC4&}1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since we wore yukata to a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a few yukata. Which do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This purple one is nice. It looks very mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember having this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:08.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mold is growing on it. The color changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess none of them work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:17.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe one of the older ones will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,These mules look really mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're Run-chan's mom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:34.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these, I might reach 1*0 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:42.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never grow up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! We took them back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The festival was today, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very nice and flowery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the festival is tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still 10 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:29.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:38.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't Yuuko-chan look lovely no matter what she wears?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Nagi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she curled her hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:44.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:54.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks are still a long way off, so why don't we spend time at the booths?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we see the mask store first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:05.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you like kids' cartoons, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:13.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we pass any shopping district booths, they'll try to give me stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:14.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A candy apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy apple...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, can I have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:26.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:27.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Tooru, you want some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:37.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, can I have some cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan's trying the ring toss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a third prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your fireworks set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We come to see fireworks, and the prize is fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:09.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,First prize, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:43.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I only have this much left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booths cost quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you might not have enough for a second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:54.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you see these kinds of things, you just have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:59.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you choose things that you can enjoy for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Katanuki{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:09.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, these things don't happen too often. Why don't we do something we can all do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:14.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you've never tried {\i1}katanuki{\i0}. It's fun, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:15.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we try, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's try some easy ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:32.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister, one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:43.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:52.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka is still eating {\i1}yakisoba{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks show will begin momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks started already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:13.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a good spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:18.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the platform! No one goes there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:22.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, that's enough {\i1}katanuki{\i0} for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! My gourd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:33.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just up these stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:38.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I kind of don't care for fireworks anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Nagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:04.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The fireworks show has now come to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:10.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please dispose of any trash in the marked bins or take it with you as you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:14.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only seeing that last part just isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:16.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got fireworks from that booth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:23.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Good job, Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:28.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A candle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:38.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there only {\i1}senko hanabi{\i0} in this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:47.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like {\i1}senko hanabi{\i0}, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:53.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:09.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:12.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei? Why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:18.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:23.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:27.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Sensei, did you come here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I didn't come here alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barkeep, another pint.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am {\i1}not{\i0} alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:53.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation sure was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:54.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:56.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:58.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We even went to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:00.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see the fireworks next year too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish my {\i1}katanuki{\i0} next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:07.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on. It was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We got hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:14.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:19.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:56.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H9E49D6&\3c&HCACFBF&}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:57.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of the end of August...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:23:58.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:00.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Copying it from someone who already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:03.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to rush my picture diary, but I don't know what the weather was like every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:06.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next A Channel: New Term
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.20,0:24:09.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we're not in elementary school...
